Time to buy a throw out arm.  They are about $15 the last time I did.  
Bentley'l should you how to install it.  Don't lose the circlip!.

In a split case tranny you have to split the case to replace the TO arm.   
Which is tons more work.   But it is also possible to weld an arm back on.


